## "TaskBuster Django Tutorial"

### This is a tutorial by Marina Mele. It is a tutorial, but also a checklist which can be referred to for every Django project to make sure you accomplish all of the tasks to get up and running. 

http://www.marinamele.com/taskbuster-django-tutorial
